data.description: This beautiful two-bedroom, one-and-a-half-bath, one-and-a-half-story home is absolutely charming. The beautiful front porch with a side gazebo is just the beginning of the curb appeal this property has. The inside is wrought with beautiful woodwork at every turn from the beautiful staircase to the double wide doorways between the formal dining room, the living room, and entry. The updated luxury vinyl planking matches the texture of the house and speaks to the care of the owners as they've modernized parts of this house while preserving its original character and beauty. The deck that is just out the back door is perfect for private evenings outside or for hosting guests. The massive garage is exactly what anyone needs no matter what they need the extra space for. In addition to the incredibly oversized shop, there is an additional dry bar mancave/entertaining space that is ready for family gatherings or simply your own incredibly spacious separate and private getaway. Don't let this beautiful opportunity go away. Call for your showing today.
